{"id":"spgr-s34.69","title":"RegisterAuthoringService accepts nil for both parameters but GetPrompts handler panics at nil store dereference","description":"RegisterAuthoringService in internal/server/authoring_handler.go accepts nil for both authoringStore and backend:

  func RegisterAuthoringService(mux *http.ServeMux, authoringStore storage.AuthoringBackend, backend storage.Backend) {
