{"id":"spgr-34l.14","title":"Duplicate stage-to-proto mapping tables in authoring package and server","description":"Two separate but identical stage-to-proto mapping tables exist: stageToProtoEnum in internal/authoring/prompts.go (line ~1000) and stageToProto in internal/server/authoring_handler.go (line ~2861). Both map the same five stage strings to the same AuthoringStage proto enum values.

