{"id":"spgr-34l.39","title":"Decompose handler builds sliceIntents with manual loop where strings.Map or a collect helper would suffice","description":"In internal/server/authoring_handler.go (lines ~2670-2676), the Decompose handler manually builds a string slice from slice intents:

