{"id":"spgr-34l.21","title":"Supersede handler generic error path does not wrap error with handler context","description":"In internal/server/authoring_handler.go, the Supersede handler has its own error handling (diff around line 2742-2747) that does NOT use the shared h.stageError() helper:

    if err := h.store.SupersedeSpec(ctx, req.Msg.Slug, req.Msg.SupersededBy, req.Msg.Reason); err != nil {
