Fix: Route SupersedeSpec errors through h.stageError() for consistency, and additionally handle ErrSpecNotFound before calling it (since stageError doesn't handle that sentinel for most callers).","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"4678+seanb4t@users.noreply.github.com","created_at":"2026-03-04T02:16:02Z","created_by":"seanb4t","updated_at":"2026-03-04T02:16:02Z","external_ref":"https://github.com/seanb4t/specgraph/pull/8"}

